---
Slots:
 -day: requested day of appointment
  restrictions: "the message may include unspecific phrases such as 'next month' or 'within a month'. If a month and day is provided, include MONTH DAY as the output. If not, output 'Unspecified X' where X is the provided description. If no mention of date is provided, do not include in the output."
 -time: requested time of appointment
  restrictions: the message may be in words, such as "afternoon preferred" or "after 10". Use the following categories [9:00-12:00, 12:00-15:00, 15:00-18:00]. Your output should only include those three slots, you may output more than one. For example, in "afternoon preferred", you would output "12:00-15:00, 15:00-18:00"
 -service: alignment, oil change, routine, tires, brakes, repair, other
  restrictions: only output the one-word categories listed under "service". the only exception to this is "other". For "other", include a brief description of the service requested
 -model: SUV, sedan, compact, electric
  restrictions: only output from the list in "model". If not specified, do not output this slot at all. 
 -year: year of car
 restrictions: only output an exact year if provided. If none, do not output this slot

Fill the slots with entities from the following message, following the instructions exactly. Output should also be in YAML format. 

Message: Hi can I make an appointment to do my winter tire changeover. Next week is best for me, Monday or Wednesday morning.

rejected:
---
-day: Unspecified: next week
-time: Unspecified: morning
-service: tires
-model: compact
-year: None
-restrictions: {}
